title: 'Shazam!' DVD/BluRay Extras Include Deleted Scenes
body:
‘Shazam!’ DVD/BluRay Extras Include Deleted Scenes

Thanks to DVD and Blu-Ray audiences have had opportunities to see deleted scenes and alternate cuts of films. In many instances, the version we see in theaters is not as good as the Director’s Cut. It has never been more true than the film Batman v. Superman: Dawn of Justice. Warner Bros. gave us a hacked up, disjointed mess in theaters, but once we saw the Ultimate Edition it was clear the movie…

summary: The cutest thing happened today because of Endgame
body:
The cutest thing happened today because of Endgame

I don’t see my brother very often, because he lives with his father. He saw Endgame yesterday and visited me today. When he left I gave him a hug and said: I love you 3000. And he said: I love you 6000 😭 It was so cute. My poor heart 😭❤
